data.description: College Hill full brick beauty newly renovated and tastefully refreshed keeping in mind the character of the home. Located on an extra deep lot with lush trees, greenspace, and plenty of room to grow. A rare find for the area with a large living room, spacious family room with a wood burning fireplace, an ensuite master bathroom, and a darling half bath on the main level. Home has brand new paint throughout - every wall, ceiling, and piece of woodwork has been painted in the last year. Cozy family room boasts rustic ceiling beams, limestone fireplace, lovely quartz dry bar, and decorative floating shelves to house all those books or decorative collectibles. Kitchen has lovely granite countertops, eating bar, and modern tile backsplash as does the 1/2 bath, and dry bar. Newly installed marble tile hearth in the living room. Updated light fixtures throughout - all selected to preserve the integrity of the home. Beautiful wood floors throughout that are in fabulous condition. Lovely and practical built ins, located in the formal dining room, off the kitchen, and the upper floor landing. The fenced backyard is a delight with a stamped concrete patio, security lighting, extra large yard with planting beds, and a 2-car garage with a separate storage space in the back. Basement has a nice rec room for the kids or a home gym and a non-conforming bonus room, large laundry/utility room, and plenty of storage. New in 2021: HVAC system, refrigerator, dishwasher, garbage disposal, upstairs bathtub resurfaced, upstairs toilets replaced. New and established landscaping, irrigated lawn. Book your showing early! It is a great find!
